## Confidence & Decay

- **High confidence**: Explicit user statements ("I love hiking", "I work at Google")
- **Lower confidence**: Implied preferences from user questions (asking many questions about a topic)
- **Low decay**: Stable facts (biographical details, long-term preferences, career, hobbies)
- **High decay**: Transient states (current project, mood, what they're reading now)

